      <title>随着出口猛增，德国陷入困境的经济迎来了“希望之光”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/germany-s-struggling-economy-gets-ray-of-hope-as-exports-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国出口在今年年初大幅增长，这表明困扰欧洲最大经济体的工业疲软可能正在缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/germany-s-struggling-economy-gets-ray-of-hope-as-exports-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 08:59:34 GMT</pubDate>
