    <item>
      <title>加州人分拆64亿美元债券以应对无家可归问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/californians-split-on-6-4-billion-bond-to-fight-homelessness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州选民在一项投票措施的早期回报上存在分歧，这项投票措施旨在借款 64 亿美元，为新住房提供资金，并扩大对无家可归者的治疗计划，特别是那些与精神疾病和毒瘾作斗争的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/californians-split-on-6-4-billion-bond-to-fight-homelessness</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 08:28:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯无人机袭击导致乌克兰西部地区断电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/russian-drone-attack-cuts-power-in-western-ukraine-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯对乌克兰发动了三周多来最大规模的无人机袭击，能源基础设施遭到破坏，导致西部赫梅利尼茨基地区部分地区 14,000 名消费者断电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/russian-drone-attack-cuts-power-in-western-ukraine-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 08:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚和东盟敦促在南海紧张局势中保持克制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/australia-asean-urge-restraint-amid-tensions-in-south-china-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚和东南亚国家对南海“危及和平”的行为发出警告，并呼吁保持克制。一天前，中国和菲律宾船只相撞，引发了争议航道新的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/australia-asean-urge-restraint-amid-tensions-in-south-china-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 07:33:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
